text: Just as a huge warning, if for any reason you’re using @FedEx, request that items do not go to the Hornsey depot. A high-value parcel has not been delivered since Weds and was last scanned at that depot. Any update yet @FedExHelp? Would like to find out where it is.
Anyone want to pick this up @FedExHelp @FedEx? At all?

@OwleSchreame @FedEx @FedExHelp There’s some stuff going on behind the scenes, but the actual issue is as yet unresolved. Not much communication from their customer service centre but I’m hoping that’s because they’re frantically trying to locate this high-value parcel.

@artbaretta Hi, this is April.  Thank you for contacting the U.S. Social Customer Service team. Please reach out to @FedExHelpEU for assistance in your location. 
https://t.co/6uE0yQ8ibI

@FedExHelp @FedExHelpEU Hi April, thanks for getting in touch. I’ve already done this and have been in touch with the UK customer service AND tried the depot itself. This is a really serious issue so I wanted to cover all bases. I understand you’re US only so I found the EU one shortly after. Thanks.
